The paper discusses market dynamics and game theory, which are typically categorized under cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics). The use of the level $k$ model and the analogy to AI and control theory suggest that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. The paper also discusses convergence rates, which falls under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
